00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:34,930
[ROAD HOME]

3
00:01:35,250 --> 00:01:37,700
[Episode 28]

4
00:01:38,979 --> 00:01:39,420
No way.

5
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:43,600
Why is everyone asking me to be sensible?

6
00:01:51,650 --> 00:01:51,990
Bye.

7
00:01:52,770 --> 00:01:54,050
I'll contact you after the training.

8
00:01:54,050 --> 00:01:55,979
Lu Chen, if you dare to hang up on me,

9
00:01:59,050 --> 00:02:00,510
there will be no next time.

10
00:02:00,980 --> 00:02:02,510
You will never see me again.

11
00:02:08,780 --> 00:02:12,430
[Year 2018]

12
00:02:48,940 --> 00:02:51,960
Do you... remember who I am?

13
00:02:52,890 --> 00:02:53,329
Yes.

14
00:02:55,110 --> 00:02:57,640
I'll remember you even if you turn into ashes.

15
00:03:37,700 --> 00:03:38,420
This year,

16
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,770
I managed to get back to Lu Chen.

17
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:44,160
We've got a legal marriage certificate.

18
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:46,020
Although we haven't had the ceremony,

19
00:03:46,020 --> 00:03:47,220
we've had a daughter.

20
00:03:48,220 --> 00:03:49,480
She was born in Qining.

21
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:52,700
It's thousands of miles away from Beijing.

22
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:11,900
Stay still.

23
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,260
Thank you for your effort.

24
00:04:20,310 --> 00:04:21,620
He's your son-in-law.

25
00:04:22,019 --> 00:04:23,620
Do you have to be that polite?

26
00:04:23,860 --> 00:04:25,320
We should always be polite

27
00:04:25,820 --> 00:04:26,680
to a hero.

28
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:28,840
This is my profession.

29
00:04:28,930 --> 00:04:29,660
It's my duty.

30
00:04:32,930 --> 00:04:33,590
He's Dr. Xu.

31
00:04:35,700 --> 00:04:37,300
We've met a few times before.

32
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,659
The first time was at the airport.

33
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:41,390
Yes.

34
00:04:42,250 --> 00:04:43,380
When we first met,

35
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:46,290
did you regard me as your rival in love?

36
00:04:47,420 --> 00:04:48,100
It's rare to see her

37
00:04:48,100 --> 00:04:49,630
smile like that to someone.

38
00:04:50,740 --> 00:04:52,200
There's a reason for that.

39
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:55,710
Gui Xiao and I are friends in need.

40
00:04:57,450 --> 00:04:58,650
Do you want to hear it?

41
00:04:58,670 --> 00:05:00,270
I'd like to hear the details.

42
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,100
It's rare for Captain Lu

43
00:05:02,100 --> 00:05:03,960
to have time to listen to stories.

44
00:05:04,380 --> 00:05:06,530
I'd been lying in the hospital bed before this.

45
00:05:06,530 --> 00:05:08,530
Now I can finally get some fresh air.

46
00:05:09,380 --> 00:05:10,710
Enjoy your conversation.

47
00:05:10,710 --> 00:05:11,770
I'll check on Xiao.

48
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:12,270
Okay.

49
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:14,520
If you don't mind,

50
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:16,790
please send him back to the ward later.

51
00:05:25,860 --> 00:05:28,310
What do you want to know?

52
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:32,460
How did you suffer?

53
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:36,860
On the year

54
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:38,659
Gui Xiao's parents divorced...

55
00:05:39,490 --> 00:05:40,409
To be exact,

56
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:43,480
the year they decided to live apart,

57
00:05:44,820 --> 00:05:45,810
I was an intern.

58
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:53,040
[Year 2011]

59
00:06:09,230 --> 00:06:09,830
Thank you.

60
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:15,180
Are you upset because of your family?

61
00:06:15,180 --> 00:06:16,510
Is it a serious illness?

62
00:06:17,140 --> 00:06:17,650
No.

63
00:06:19,300 --> 00:06:21,030
I had a fight with my boyfriend.

64
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:24,990
That's a good reason.

65
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:29,720
It's best if you are crying about that

66
00:06:29,740 --> 00:06:30,670
in the hospital.

67
00:06:31,340 --> 00:06:32,570
It's much better

68
00:06:32,610 --> 00:06:34,340
than crying for other reasons.

69
00:06:35,659 --> 00:06:36,659
That makes sense.

70
00:06:46,230 --> 00:06:48,690
It's not worth fighting over trivialities.

71
00:06:51,020 --> 00:06:52,820
My girlfriend is about your age.

72
00:06:54,340 --> 00:06:55,870
She's my childhood friend.

73
00:06:55,940 --> 00:06:57,570
Since she was young, she has had a disease

74
00:06:57,570 --> 00:06:58,700
that can't be cured.

75
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:02,010
The older she grows, the more serious her illness is.

76
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:04,180
But she seldom cries.

77
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:07,790
She's very optimistic.

78
00:07:10,700 --> 00:07:12,140
But every time we talked about how

79
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:13,940
she might leave earlier than me,

80
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:15,300
she would cry.

81
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:25,620
When I saw

82
00:07:25,620 --> 00:07:26,660
Gui Xiao cry,

83
00:07:27,660 --> 00:07:29,190
I thought of my girlfriend.

84
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:31,180
When my girlfriend cries,

85
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:32,000
she's just like her.

86
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,460
She's also used to weeping

87
00:07:33,770 --> 00:07:35,030
without saying a word.

88
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:37,120
Be careful.

89
00:07:38,420 --> 00:07:39,020
Thank you.

90
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,640
After that, her mother was hospitalized.

91
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:43,850
And she asked me for help.

92
00:07:43,850 --> 00:07:45,520
We've become close since then.

93
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:46,210
And eventually, we've become

94
00:07:46,210 --> 00:07:47,610
bosom friends for years.

95
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:49,409
She and my wife are very close.

96
00:07:49,409 --> 00:07:51,470
They keep no secrets from each other.

97
00:07:52,220 --> 00:07:53,780
You married your childhood sweetheart?

98
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:54,790
What'd you expect?

99
00:07:54,790 --> 00:07:55,920
Who else could it be?

100
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,100
Before we got married,

101
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:01,780
my mom had once asked me

102
00:08:01,780 --> 00:08:03,020
to go to her room.

103
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:04,450
I thought

104
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,160
she had regretted

105
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:08,350
and wanted to stop me from getting married.

106
00:08:08,350 --> 00:08:09,860
But later, she took out a bank card,

107
00:08:09,860 --> 00:08:11,860
saying it was her savings for years.

108
00:08:11,890 --> 00:08:13,530
She advised me to be nice to my wife.

109
00:08:13,530 --> 00:08:15,590
She said, â€œIf you dare to cheat on her,

110
00:08:15,910 --> 00:08:18,110
I will be the first to turn against you.â€

111
00:08:19,540 --> 00:08:22,270
What happened after that? How is she feeling now?

112
00:08:23,220 --> 00:08:24,020
Same as usual.

113
00:08:25,810 --> 00:08:26,640
The last time I met

114
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,440
with Gui Xiao,

115
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:29,710
I borrowed money from her

116
00:08:29,940 --> 00:08:30,870
to buy medicine.

117
00:08:35,730 --> 00:08:37,789
My wife chose this. What do you think?

118
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,640
I have one too.

119
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:42,380
But because of work,

120
00:08:42,530 --> 00:08:44,059
I can't wear it all the time.

121
00:08:46,540 --> 00:08:47,600
Cherish your love.

122
00:08:48,260 --> 00:08:48,790
I mean it.

123
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:51,760
Gui Xiao loves you wholeheartedly.

124
00:08:53,140 --> 00:08:53,540
I will.

125
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:55,700
Good luck to you, too.

126
00:08:55,700 --> 00:08:56,140
Sure.

127
00:08:59,700 --> 00:09:00,700
Are you talking about something serious?

128
00:09:00,700 --> 00:09:01,360
You may continue.

129
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,490
We'll wait outside.

130
00:09:02,900 --> 00:09:04,430
It's okay. We're done talking.

131
00:09:04,430 --> 00:09:05,780
I'm going back to Beijing soon.

132
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:06,620
I have a lot of work to do in the hospital.

133
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:08,020
There is a limited workforce.

134
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:09,080
See you in Beijing.

135
00:09:09,130 --> 00:09:09,460
Okay.

136
00:09:09,650 --> 00:09:11,850
Take your wife along with you next time.

137
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:20,360
You still have a friend

138
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:21,020
who we don't know

139
00:09:21,020 --> 00:09:22,030
in Qining?

140
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:24,660
You sound like my wife.

141
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:27,020
I think so too.

142
00:09:27,900 --> 00:09:28,400
Go away.

143
00:09:30,140 --> 00:09:31,420
He's Gui Xiao's friend,

144
00:09:31,420 --> 00:09:32,380
a gynecologist.

145
00:09:32,380 --> 00:09:33,140
This time,

146
00:09:33,140 --> 00:09:34,600
he specially came here with Gui Xiao.

147
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:36,030
Her friend?

148
00:09:36,490 --> 00:09:37,480
They came here together.

149
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,010
Aren't you jealous of that?

150
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:41,160
They're just ordinary friends.

151
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,650
Why should I be jealous?

152
00:09:45,310 --> 00:09:46,790
As a married man,

153
00:09:46,820 --> 00:09:47,980
let me analyze

154
00:09:47,980 --> 00:09:48,910
his psychology.

155
00:09:49,190 --> 00:09:50,850
He must be jealous, without any doubt.

156
00:09:50,850 --> 00:09:52,090
What does being jealous mean?

157
00:09:52,090 --> 00:09:53,090
It means you care.

158
00:09:53,750 --> 00:09:55,010
A little jealousy is enjoyable.

159
00:09:55,010 --> 00:09:55,880
Right, Zhong?

160
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:58,160
I think so.

161
00:09:58,820 --> 00:09:59,930
What do you mean?

162
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:02,380
I mean, I'm always late catching on

163
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:03,380
and seldom jealous.

164
00:10:03,380 --> 00:10:04,620
My wife and I went to college together.

165
00:10:04,620 --> 00:10:06,460
We have a lot of friends in common.

166
00:10:06,460 --> 00:10:08,010
Okay, let me summarize.

167
00:10:08,420 --> 00:10:10,710
Our deputy captain is always jealous,

168
00:10:11,510 --> 00:10:12,910
while Zhong is generous.

169
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:13,360
No.

170
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:15,120
I'm analyzing Captain Lu.

171
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:16,830
I don't need your analysis.

172
00:10:17,090 --> 00:10:18,220
That's right.

173
00:10:20,610 --> 00:10:22,340
You were near death once again.

174
00:10:22,460 --> 00:10:24,060
I was almost scared to death.

175
00:10:24,340 --> 00:10:25,580
I thought a lot

176
00:10:25,900 --> 00:10:27,430
when you were in operation.

177
00:10:27,730 --> 00:10:30,460
Forget it. I'll stop saying those ominous words.

178
00:10:31,540 --> 00:10:33,340
It's good that you've survived.

179
00:10:33,700 --> 00:10:35,780
Every day is a good day starting from that.

180
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:36,160
Yes.

181
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:39,060
One is bound for good fortune after surviving a catastrophe.

182
00:10:39,060 --> 00:10:40,050
You have had good fortune.

183
00:10:40,050 --> 00:10:41,980
You had a daughter when you woke up.

184
00:10:42,060 --> 00:10:43,590
By the way, how is your wife?

185
00:10:44,770 --> 00:10:45,430
She's fine.

186
00:10:46,620 --> 00:10:48,020
Her life was at stake too.

187
00:10:50,180 --> 00:10:51,140
The baby was just born.

188
00:10:51,140 --> 00:10:52,640
And she's lying alone in the ward.

189
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,910
It's not appropriate for us to go there.

190
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:56,480
We've asked the nurse to pass on some supplements to her.

191
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:56,880
How about this?

192
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:58,850
When the child gets older,

193
00:10:58,930 --> 00:11:00,590
take her back here to visit us.

194
00:11:00,740 --> 00:11:01,940
Sounds great.

195
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:02,780
Take her back to us.

196
00:11:02,780 --> 00:11:05,510
When I go back to Tianwen after being discharged,

197
00:11:05,780 --> 00:11:07,380
it will be another farewell.

198
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:09,300
We've been discussing this.

199
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:10,820
When you are discharged,

200
00:11:10,820 --> 00:11:11,980
we may not have time.

201
00:11:12,380 --> 00:11:13,700
That's why we're all here today

202
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,430
to visit you.

203
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,980
After saying goodbye,

204
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:17,150
again and again,

205
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,340
everyone feels upset.

206
00:11:19,700 --> 00:11:20,540
Yes, Captain Lu.

207
00:11:20,540 --> 00:11:21,140
Indeed.

208
00:11:22,380 --> 00:11:23,040
Captain Lu.

209
00:11:23,180 --> 00:11:24,700
When I have a long vacation,

210
00:11:24,700 --> 00:11:25,920
I'll take my wife to visit you.

211
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:26,340
OK.

212
00:11:27,140 --> 00:11:27,760
I suggest

213
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:29,340
if we have another mission next time,

214
00:11:29,340 --> 00:11:30,050
we all

215
00:11:30,820 --> 00:11:32,750
apply for a transfer of Captain Lu.

216
00:11:33,220 --> 00:11:34,150
That's not good.

217
00:11:34,210 --> 00:11:35,780
You're talking about important missions.

218
00:11:35,780 --> 00:11:37,600
Captain Lu has a wife and a daughter.

219
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,550
We can't let him go on a mission every time.

220
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:40,880
I'll do it when he comes.

221
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:42,310
If so, who will take the credit?

222
00:11:42,310 --> 00:11:43,320
I'm okay with that.

223
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,190
I'm alone.

224
00:11:44,970 --> 00:11:46,430
My only son is with him.

225
00:11:46,510 --> 00:11:47,370
He is in charge.

226
00:11:48,650 --> 00:11:49,710
Give me your phone.

227
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:51,350
Do you want to call your wife?

228
00:11:53,340 --> 00:11:54,260
I'm calling someone

229
00:11:54,260 --> 00:11:55,890
who really

230
00:11:55,890 --> 00:11:57,090
takes care of his son.

231
00:11:58,330 --> 00:11:59,140
Who is it?

232
00:11:59,940 --> 00:12:01,900
I know, it's Duan Rou.

233
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:03,020
Shut up!

234
00:12:03,410 --> 00:12:04,670
Don't be shy, captain.

235
00:12:06,070 --> 00:12:07,330
Show respect to our captain.

236
00:12:07,330 --> 00:12:08,530
Come at me if you want.

237
00:12:09,250 --> 00:12:10,980
I don't need you to cover for me.

238
00:12:11,340 --> 00:12:13,470
Even if I'm in a relationship, so what?

239
00:12:13,580 --> 00:12:13,940
What?

240
00:12:13,940 --> 00:12:16,880
How much worse am I than Captain Lu?

241
00:12:17,530 --> 00:12:18,900
I had a son before he did.

242
00:12:19,210 --> 00:12:20,020
Fine.

243
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,010
Hold on a second.

244
00:12:21,420 --> 00:12:22,620
Did she agree?

245
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:26,120
No, we are already adults.

246
00:12:26,680 --> 00:12:27,950
J-Just once will do.

247
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:29,530
What?

248
00:12:29,780 --> 00:12:31,220
You haven't confessed to her yet?

249
00:12:31,220 --> 00:12:31,940
Confess what?

250
00:12:31,940 --> 00:12:33,290
Say you like her.

251
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:35,380
How can I

252
00:12:35,860 --> 00:12:37,260
say that out of my mouth?

253
00:12:37,540 --> 00:12:39,220
You're so childish.

254
00:12:39,220 --> 00:12:40,580
Love is in your heart.

255
00:12:40,700 --> 00:12:41,580
Deputy Captain,

256
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:42,990
write a report next year

257
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:44,180
to replace Captain Qin.

258
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:45,050
He's such a coward.

259
00:12:45,050 --> 00:12:46,380
Really, Captain Qin.

260
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:48,830
I'm looking down on you for the first time.

261
00:12:49,660 --> 00:12:50,990
You don't confess to her

262
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:52,360
but expect her to say it?

263
00:13:01,570 --> 00:13:02,230
Qin Mingyu?

264
00:13:02,970 --> 00:13:03,830
I'm Lu Yanchen.

265
00:13:04,580 --> 00:13:05,240
Captain Lu?

266
00:13:06,690 --> 00:13:07,550
How is Gui Xiao?

267
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:08,920
She's fine.

268
00:13:09,380 --> 00:13:10,740
She gave birth to a daughter.

269
00:13:10,740 --> 00:13:12,470
Both of them are safe and sound.

270
00:13:14,180 --> 00:13:14,910
That's good.

271
00:13:15,830 --> 00:13:17,020
You called me all of a sudden,

272
00:13:17,020 --> 00:13:19,080
so I thought something had happened.

273
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:21,960
There is one thing.

274
00:13:24,730 --> 00:13:25,590
My l-leg.

275
00:13:26,020 --> 00:13:27,080
I'm still injured.

276
00:13:28,090 --> 00:13:28,750
Lu Yanchen.

277
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:29,720
What is it?

278
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:31,650
As long as I can do it,

279
00:13:32,020 --> 00:13:32,810
tell me,

280
00:13:32,930 --> 00:13:34,460
and I'll get it done for you.

281
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:35,780
I'm glad to hear that.

282
00:13:36,860 --> 00:13:37,720
We're a family.

283
00:13:38,300 --> 00:13:39,410
I'm close to Gui Xiao.

284
00:13:39,410 --> 00:13:40,940
I treat her family as my own.

285
00:13:41,060 --> 00:13:43,520
Qin Mingyu has something urgent to tell you.

286
00:13:44,940 --> 00:13:45,230
He?

287
00:13:48,660 --> 00:13:49,190
Get lost!

288
00:13:50,860 --> 00:13:51,320
This...

289
00:13:51,680 --> 00:13:52,100
Duan Rou.

